      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-Vanos variable valve timing system. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis dynamics remain sharp, benefiting from documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension setup. While the exterior shows honest signs of road use consistent with its age, the mechanical components are robust, offering the visceral analog feedback and 8,000 RPM redline that define this chassis. A well-sorted, driver-focused example with high mechanical integrity.",
